{"type":"header","kind":"domain","name":"vsco","mk":2,"perspective":"peer","origin_repo":"lumiere","consumers":["n6-architecture"],"goal":"hexa-vsco surface — physical-limit pro photo editor (verb: EDITS-LIBRARY-DISCOVER, sister to camera APPLIES). Full VSCO feature parity (200+ filter library / HSL / tone curve / recipe / Studio / Discover / Free vs Pro) PLUS 7 alien-grade-10 differentiators: LPIPS ≤ 0.15 / SSIM ≥ 0.95 / PSNR ≥ 35 dB mathematical bounds + 16.67 ms editor latency + 30-min FILTER-ALGEBRA inverse-problem auto-generation + algebra plaintext Recipe + on-device privacy + 7 physics-based tools (Hurter-Driffield 1890 / Wiener 1949 / Cox 1955 / Planck 1900 / cos⁴θ / MacAdam 1942 / CIE 1931) + open marketplace 70% creator royalty. Internal dependency: filter_algebra engine layer (sister .roadmap.filter_algebra cond.2/3). F-VSCO-MVP-1..5 falsifier closure vs iPhone 15 Pro + cloud-sync 99.999% reliability.","required_conditions":[{"id":"vsco.cond.1","desc":"Spec absorbed + 21-section template (own#15 HARD) + own#33 ai-native-verify-pattern Block A-G + 7 differentiators framing","verifier":{"type":"script","path":"docs/vsco/hexa-vsco.md","exit_zero_means_met":true,"status_emit":"§7.1 Block A-G + own#15 21-section + 7 differentiator IPS framing PASS"},"status":"met","evidence":["docs/vsco/hexa-vsco.md (spec absorbed from n6-architecture, alien-grade 10 PHYSICAL-LIMIT)"],"blocker_reason":""},{"id":"vsco.cond.2","desc":"Editor surface — 200+ filter library browser + HSL panel + tone curve + Recipe (algebra plaintext expression like `f = portra ∘ vignette(0.3) ∘ grain(0.2)`) + Studio + Discover tab + Free/Pro tier gate","verifier":{"type":"script","path":".github/workflows/ios.yml","exit_zero_means_met":true,"status_emit":"AtelierPreviewTests PASS — Forge → Atelier cross-domain wire renders before/after through FilterAlgebra runtime"},"status":"partial","evidence":["Sources/Lumiere/Studio/Atelier/AtelierPreviewRenderer.swift (mk4-B Forge → Atelier wire — RecipeParser → FilterComposition → CIContext.createCGImage → UIImage)","Sources/Lumiere/Studio/AtelierView.swift (10-of-50 library list with tappable rows + sheet preview + before/after swatch + RecipeShareCodec demo)","Tests/LumiereTests/AtelierPreviewTests.swift (5 cases: extent / valid roundtrip / unknown primitive / empty / 50-recipe parse audit)","commit c3fb1ba — mk4-B Forge → Atelier preview cross-wire"],"blocker_reason":"Cross-domain runtime wire structurally connected (LibraryFilter recipe → FilterComposition → rendered preview). Full editor surface (HSL panel / tone curve UI / Recipe Studio / Discover tab / Free vs Pro tier gate) is mk5; PHPickerViewController user-photo input replaces the fixed gradient sample at mk5."},{"id":"vsco.cond.3","desc":"50 inaugural filters auto-generated via FILTER-ALGEBRA inverse problem (30-min batch from N=5 reference image pairs each, vs VSCO 1-2-week artist labor)","verifier":{"type":"script","path":".github/workflows/ios.yml","exit_zero_means_met":true,"status_emit":"AtelierTests.fiftyInaugural PASS (≥ 50 filters)"},"status":"partial","evidence":["Sources/Lumiere/Studio/Atelier/AtelierLibrary.swift (50 hand-curated filters with Forge-grammar Recipes — closes F-VSCO-MVP-2 ≥ 50 structurally)","Sources/Lumiere/Studio/Atelier/LibraryFilter.swift (value type)","Tests/LumiereTests/AtelierTests.swift (fiftyInaugural + uniqueIDs + nonEmptyMetadata)","commit 6f62414 — mk3-C/atelier"],"blocker_reason":"50-count threshold met structurally with hand-curated Recipes; auto-generation from N=5 reference pairs depends on filter_algebra.cond.3 (inverse-problem CLI, mk4)."},{"id":"vsco.cond.4","desc":"Recipe URL share-load roundtrip — plaintext algebra + URL-safe base64 encoder/decoder + parser idempotence test ≥ 95% across 1000 transactions","verifier":{"type":"script","path":".github/workflows/ios.yml","exit_zero_means_met":true,"status_emit":"AtelierTests.codecRoundTrip10 + codecMalformedURL + codecMissingRecipe + encodedURLShape PASS"},"status"